data.value:
This is the enhanced version of SotaJoe's original EASEncoder on GitHub: https://github.com/SotaJoe/EAS-Encoder This enhanced version includes some more features such as the National location codes which aren't in the original EASEncoder, the addition of some more event codes, and the addition of the capability to encode an EAS message from raw data. This encoder is made by Wolf20482.
You can use this software to create EAS messages for EAS mock videos or to test your EAS decoder.
WARNING - DO NOT RELY ON THIS SOFTWARE WHEN A LIFE-THREATENING SITUATION IS OCCURRING! THIS SOFTWARE GENERATES VALID EAS MESSAGES. IF YOU PLAY THESE MESSAGES OVER THE AIR, IT CAN AND WILL CAUSE MASS PANIC. MISUSE OF THE EAS TONES IS A FEDERAL OFFENSE AND CAN LEAD TO HEFTY FINES OR EVEN JAIL TIME. THE CREATOR OF THIS SOFTWARE IS NOT RESPONSIBLE FOR ANY MISUSE OF THESE TONES.
